                            <comment id="14141549" author="stack" created="Fri, 19 Sep 2014 23:33:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried it. It works if I do this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;HADOOP_HOME=~/hadoop-2.6.0-CRC-SNAPSHOT ./bin/hbase --config ~/conf_hbase org.jruby.Main bin/shutdown_regionserver.rb c2021.halxg.cloudera.com:16020&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thats how you&apos;d do it &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=patrickwhite&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;patrickwhite&quot;&gt;Patrick White&lt;/a&gt;?  If so, I&apos;ll add a little note to head of script on commit.  Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
